description:
Afrojack - FORGET THE WORLD [Deluxe Edition] (2014)



Grammy award-winning DJ & Producer, Afrojack, releases his debut album Forget The World, containing the global hit single, 'Ten Feet Tall' featuring Wrabel on Def Jam Recordings. Afrojack, or otherwise known as Nick van der Wall, is one of the most influential names in electronic dance music a key game changer in the genre. The album features all-star collaborations with Snoop Dogg, Sting, Wiz Khalifa, Chris Brown, and others, in addition to a remix of Do Or Die by Thirty Seconds To Mars.
